cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.CY 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the limitations of current machine learning systems and proposes a new approach to develop more intelligent systems. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper is focused on machine teaching and the development of ML systems. 
3. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper discusses the importance of creating more humane ML systems and the role of domain experts in this process. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper mentions the use of high-level knowledge constructs in making ML systems interactively teachable. 
5. cs.CY (Computers and Society) - The paper discusses the potential benefits of building ML systems by a community of experts and the inclusivity of such systems.
